    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating applied upon purchase. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple without a single crease, and the 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships\u2014full service records are organized and available for review. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a top-tier specimen that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Includes both original keys, all factory manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
